{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_02_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 3話 やっぱり負けず嫌い",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The day of the ad shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、やっぱり私\nこの仕事、自信がありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI don’t feel confident about this job at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスをするCMなんて……東京には\nもっと上手い人がいるのに、恥をかきそうで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know there’s dancing involved‚\nbut there are so many people who are better than me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.633333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり、お断りした方が\nよかったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe I should have\nturned this down…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんだ。怜はサニーピースの中で\n一番踊れてる。適任だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re the best dancer in Sunny Peace.\nI think you’re the perfect person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.266666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、他の事務所には\nもっと凄いアイドルが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But there are so many great idols\nat other agencies…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "よその子達と比べても、決して負けてなんかいない\n俺が保証する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can stand toe-to-toe with idols from any agency.\nI guarantee that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなの……単なる身内びいきですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn’t that just… favoritism?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "はっきり言おう\n今の怜に足りないのは技術じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen up‚ Rei.\nWhatever your weaknesses are‚ technique isn’t one of them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.93333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……録画して観るとあきらかに私は\nLizNoirやBIG4より劣って見えるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can’t help but feel inferior when I compare my recordings\nto that of LizNoir or the BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、今、怜が本来の自分を\n見失っているからだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you’ve\nlost sight of who you really are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリで優勝して、君達の知名度は上がった\n以前とは比べ物にならないほど注目されている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You guys have become much more well known\nsince you won the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そのせいで怜は失敗を\n恐れ過ぎてしまったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the success has\nmade you too afraid of failure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "私が失敗を恐れてる……？\nスランプはそのせい……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m afraid of failure?\nIs that why I’m in a slump?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "リフレッシュすれば改善すると思っていたけど\n怜は正面から立ち向かう方がいいと考え直したんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking maybe a change of pace would help‚\nbut in your case‚ maybe it’s better to take things head-on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.36666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、この仕事を私に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that why you assigned this job to me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、でも今後もっとプレッシャーを乗り越えなきゃ\nいけない時がくる。ここで潰れるようじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But this won’t be the last time that you’ll have to deal with pressure.\nIf this is too much for you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "待って下さい！　私、潰れてなんかいませんし\n潰れるつもりもありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait! I can handle it.\nI won’t give in to the pressure.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.66666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、現場に来ても、まだためらってるじゃないか\nせっかくのチャンスを自ら捨てようとしている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we’re already on scene‚ and you’re still feeling unsure.\nYou’re trying to throw away this valuable opportunity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "誰もやらないなんて言ってません！\nそこで見てて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never said I wouldn’t do it!\nSit down and watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、さっき私に言った言葉を\n撤回させてみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll make you take back\nwhat you just said‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私、今なら誰よりも凄いダンスが出来そうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I can dance better than anybody.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、思い切り凄いのを見せてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Great. Show me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "……っ！　言われなくても！\nスタッフのみなさん、お願いします！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…! You just wait and see!\nHi everyone‚ I’m ready to go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_botanicalgarden-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_02_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（怜には強めのコミュニケーションもいいのかもな）\n（少しかわいそうだったけどスランプは脱出したようだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Looks like Rei is the type who needs to treated tough.)\n(Maybe it was a little harsh‚ but it looks like she’s out of her slump.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.73333333333332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 500,
          "startTime": 140.13333333333333
